		<title>『フィルターバブル』を読む - remark</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://text.baldanders.info/remark/2016/05/filter-bubble/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2016-05-07:/remark/2016/05/filter-bubble/</id>
